character. They adjust to new morphs much more quickly than most
other people. Apply a +10 modifier per level for Integration
Tests and Alienation Tests.

TRAIT:::AGI Affinity
Cost: 5 CP
The character has spent a significant amount of time around
AGIs, to the point where socializing with an AGI is far easier. The
character gains a +10 modifier on Social Skill Tests against AGIs as
well as characters with the Real World Naivete trait.

